        "timestamp": "2018-08-29 22:10:07.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nfixed in https://lists.onap.org/g/onap-discuss/topic/deploy_helm_verify_job/25077611?p=,,,20,0,0,0::recentpostdate%2Fsticky,,,20,2,0,25077611",
